{"type": "article", "id": 27180, "title": "分类垃圾箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144013QJwbZxY5BLneUTyv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>很多人已经有了垃圾分类的意识，外出时会根据垃圾桶的标签进行丢弃，伦敦设计工作室 <a href=\"http://pearsonlloyd.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PearsonLloyd</a> 打算让你在家里也能做到这一点：工作室为厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 设计的 Stack 是一套分类垃圾箱，由多个塑料垃圾箱构成，采用直立堆叠的方式节省了空间。每个垃圾箱上都有一个带凹槽的滑盖，可以在凹槽上放置标签来区别每个垃圾桶的“职责”。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-rw/stack-recycling-separation-bins\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">购买链接</a>，根据容量的不同，价格为 50 到 100 英镑。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144011z0won8EcOXHKbIFr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144011kpLeEPxHo6BbCmwW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144012UzT1wvhFOLHZVW8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144012eu4PRjogXVsE7ITL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}